TAMAGAMI  "tama5's MEGAMI"

TAMAGAMI loves flowers, her best friend Morita.
The two of us can do anything. Our imagination is limitless.
We love all artists who support each other and collecters who love arts.

This artwork complies with the MEGAMI art license.
I want to express my respect and appreciation for MEGAMI project.
